# 🚀 Project Management App

A full-stack Project Management application built to manage tasks efficiently with authentication and project tracking features.

---

## ✨ Features

* 🔐 User Authentication (Login / Signup)
* 📁 Create New Projects
* 📋 View All Projects
* ✅ Update Project Status (Pending / Completed)

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

* **Frontend:** React (Vite)
* **Backend:** Node.js, Express
* **Database:** MongoDB

---

## 📦 Installation & Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/amitvishwakarma8881/Project_Management.git
cd Project_Management
npm install
npm run dev
```

